metadata.name: Tree of Wonder
metadata.description: The Tree of Wonder stands tall and proud, a beacon of light in a world that is often dark and bleak.  Its branches reach up to the sky, a symbol of growth and resilience in the face of adversity.  Despite standing alone in a world that is hostile and unforgiving, the Tree of Wonder remains strong and steadfast - its roots digging deep into the earth, anchoring it to the ground.  The leaves rustle in the breeze, a whisper of hope to those who are lost and seeking guidance.  The Tree of Wonder is a reminder to us all that, no matter how difficult the journey may be, there is always the possibility of growth, strength, and resilience.
